{"sections":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Since you have learned how OUDS works with theme, themeable view, components, tuning and view modifiers, it is time now to discover some online resources."}]}],"title":"Going further with more resources","chapter":"Go further with more ressources","image":"ic_theme_intro.png","estimatedTimeInMinutes":10,"kind":"hero","backgroundImage":"ic_theme_intro.png"},{"kind":"tasks","tasks":[{"stepsSection":[{"caption":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can get it at "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/"}]}],"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The iOS technical documentation is available online. It has been generated from all the Swift DocC documentation written in the Swift Package.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"You will find several catalogs (as many as librairies) with details about everyhting: components, tokens, themes, providers, etc.","type":"text"}]}],"media":"tutorial-discovery-6-1.png","runtimePreview":null,"type":"step","code":null},{"type":"step","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The whole design system is documented and available online. You can find everything about components, tokens, guidelines and principles of OUDS."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"icon finder","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" is also available there to get icons for your projects."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"media":"tutorial-discovery-6-2.png","caption":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Go to the website and learn things at ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/","type":"reference","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"}],"code":null,"runtimePreview":null},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OUDS iOS provides also a wiki attached to its GitHub repository. The wiki is a public base of knowledge with plenty of things: available API, technicala architecture, tips about processes, tests, conventions and toolings."}]}],"media":"tutorial-discovery-6-3.png","code":null,"runtimePreview":null,"caption":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Have a look ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios\/wiki","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" to discover how OUDS works.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"step"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For technical reasons the "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" GitHub repository does not embed the source code of the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"design system toolbox","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" app. In fact this app and all its snapshots for tests increases a lot the size of the repository."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"media":"tutorial-discovery-6-4.png","caption":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"To get the source code of this showcase app, go to its dedicated GitHub repository at ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios-design-system-toolbox","type":"reference","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"}],"code":null,"runtimePreview":null,"type":"step"},{"runtimePreview":null,"media":"tutorial-discovery-6-5.png","caption":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Do not hesitate to "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios\/issues","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios\/discussions"},{"type":"text","text":"!"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"step","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OUDS is open source, public and uses GitHub as forge. Thus, you will find common things inside the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios"},{"text":" GitHub repository.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"code":null}],"contentSection":[{"mediaPosition":"trailing","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Xcode can use the Swift DocC documentation of OUDS, and this documentation is used to build a static web site."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"But there are also other resources which can be useful for you.","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"contentAndMedia"}],"anchor":"More-resources","title":"More resources"}]}],"kind":"project","metadata":{"title":"Going further with more resources","category":"Orange Unified Design System","categoryPathComponent":"Table-Of-Contents-(onboarding)","role":"project"},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-onboarding-4-going-further","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/tutorials\/oudsthemescontract\/tutorial-onboarding-4-going-further"]}],"hierarchy":{"modules":[{"reference":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/Table-Of-Contents-(onboarding)\/Import-of-the-Swift-Package-and-choose-its-librairies","projects":[{"sections":[{"kind":"task","reference":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-onboarding-1-package-and-librairies#Import-the-Swift-Package-and-the-libraries"},{"kind":"assessment","reference":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-onboarding-1-package-and-librairies#Check-Your-Understanding"}],"reference":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-onboarding-1-package-and-librairies"}]},{"reference":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/Table-Of-Contents-(onboarding)\/Define-information-cards","projects":[{"reference":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-onboarding-2-nice-and-clea